short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: End the tab search for playing music after Focusmate Sessions. This Extension mutes/unmutes music based on Focusmate mute status.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This App automatically mutes every other tab, if your Focusmate Session is unmuted.
E.g. when you want to speak with the other person you don't need to search through all you tabs.
